# Contributing to ZkLite

Thank you for your interest in contributing to **ZkLite**!  
We welcome contributions of all kinds â€” code, documentation, examples, ideas, and bug reports.

ZkLite aims to make zero-knowledge proofs on Zcash accessible without deep cryptography expertise, and your help makes that possible.

